ls, India) - Borsara post (Bangladesh)\n** [[West Garo Hills district#Economy|West Garo Hills]] - [[Baksiganj Upazila|Bakshiganj]] via [[West Garo Hills district#Mahendraganj international border crossing|Mahendraganj]] crossing on [[National Highway 217 (India)|NH12]] \n** [[Tura, Meghalaya|Tura]]-[[Nalitabari Upazila|Nalitabari]] via [[Dalu, Meghalaya|Dalu]] crossing on [[National Highway 217 (India)|NH217]] (West Garo Hills, India) and Nakugaon post (Bangladesh)\n** [[West Khasi Hills district|Shellabazar]] (West Khasi Hills district) - Sunamganj(Sylhet division)\n** [[South Garo Hills district|Gasuapara]] (South Garo Hills district)- Karoitol (Mymansing division)\n** Meghalaya non-functional LCS are:\n*** [[Mawsynram|Ryngku]] (East Khasi Hills district) - Kalibari (Sonamganj division)\n*** [[Balat, Meghalaya|Balat]] (East Khasi Hills district) - Dolura (Sylhet division)\n* [[Tripura]]\n** [[Sipahijala district|Srimantapur]] ([[Sipahijala district]]) - Bibir Bazar (Comilla division), became operational in January 2016.<ref name=lcs2>[https://bdnews24.com/bangladesh/2016/01/07/tripura-opens-new-land-customs-station-along-bangladesh-border Srimantapur LCS opens]</ref> \n** [[Dhalai district|Dhalaighat]] ([[Dhalai district]]) - Kumarghat (Sunamganj division) \n** [[Khowai]]ghat ([[West Tripura district]]) - Balla (Habiganj division)  \n** [[Manu, Tripura|Manu]] (Dhalai district) - Chatlapur (Sylhet division )\n** [[South Tripura district|Muhurighat]] ([[South Tripura district]]) -  Belonia (Feni division )\n** [[North Tripura district|Old Ragnabazar]] ([[North Tripura district]]) - Betul (Fultali) (Sylhet division)\n* [[Mizoram]]\n** Kawarpuchiah integrated checkpost, opened in Oct 2017 by Prime Minister Narendra Modi.<ref name=pm1>[http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/news/national/india-opens-two-border-crossing-points-with-myanmar-bangladesh/article9883216.ece India opens two border crossing points with Myanmar, Bangladesh]</ref>\n** Non-functional LCS in Mizoram: